title: Jed Brophy, actor, The Lord of the Rings & The Hobbit - Interview
description: Jed Brophy has played Nori the dwarf, a Ringwraith, an elf, a Rider of Rohan, and two of the most memorable orcs in the Middle-earth films.  Join us for what is sure to be a fun conversation about Jed's time in Middle-earth!
